    <description>
        <p>
            Track your music listening history from many different sources:
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li>Spotify</li>
            <li>Plex (Tautulli)</li>
            <li>Any subsonic-based music player (Airsonic or Navidrome)</li>
            <li>Jellyfin</li>
            <li>WebScrobbler</li>
            <li>Mopidy</li>
            <li>JRiver</li>
            <li>Kodi</li>
            <li>Webscrobbler</li>
            <li>Youtube Music</li>
            <li>MPRIS (linux desktop)</li>
            <li>Google Cast (Chromecast)</li>
            <li>Musikcube</li>
            <li>MPDF (Music Player Daemon)</li>
            <li>VLC</li>
        </ul>
        <p>and consolidate your listens (scrobbles) into one or more scrobbling servers/services:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Maloja</li>
            <li>Last.fm</li>
            <li>Listenbrainz</li>
        </ul>
        <p>multi-scrobbler requires some configuration before use. Please visit the website or help links below to get started.</p>
    </description>
